title: Ali Jadoon wins NA-17 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Ali Khan Jadoon has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-17 Abbottabad-II by securing 97,177 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Mohabbat Khan of Pakistan Muslim League- Nawaz, who bagged 44,522 votes.
The overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 44.37 percent.
